title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 300-1.4 - Territorial application
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 300-1.4 - Territorial application

State Regulations

The provisions of this Chapter shall be effective
within, upon, under, and in the airspace above all State property that is
presently or shall in the future be under the jurisdiction, custody or control
of the office. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
300-1.4

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
